        <h6>MongoDB Connection Issues</h6>
        <ol>
          <li>Check that MongoDB is running on your system</li>
          <li>Verify the connection string in your .env file</li>
          <li>Ensure network connectivity to your MongoDB instance</li>
          <li>Check MongoDB logs for any errors</li>
        </ol>
        <h6>General Troubleshooting</h6>
        <ol>
          <li>Restart the dashboard application</li>
          <li>Check the console logs for more information</li>
          <li>Verify all required environment variables are set</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div> 